						               													<description>In your hands you have an investigative case that you can play alone or with friends. It takes little space, a bit of time and a lot of ingenuity. &amp;#10;But remember, one case leads to another!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Six chapters for six compact boxes to carry with you in every situation: the box itself contains the rules of the game, and along with the deck of cards contained in it, it will be enough to get all the clues necessary to the resolution!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;MiniCrimes is a cooperative investigative game in which you'll put your observation and deduction skills to the test to solve a mysterious case. You'll analyze a crime scene and up to 10 clues. &amp;#10;Choose carefully and solve the mystery!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;'In Mini Crimes: La fine dei giochi' (&amp;quot;Mini Crimes: The end of the games&amp;quot;), a fan of comics, toys and science fiction is found dead in his house, hit on the head by a vase.&amp;#10;How can a simple person loved by all make such a terrible end?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
